atel%2Famp_articleshow%2F118520868.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BMercedes%20For%20Posts%26quot%3B%3A%20Sena%20Leader's%20'Corruption'%20Jab%20At%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EShiv%20Sena%20leader%20Neelam%20Gorhe's%20claim%20on%20allotment%20of%20posts%20in%20the%20erstwhile%20undivided%20Sena%20led%20by%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20after%20gifting%20Mercedes%20cars%20has%20caused%20a%20row%20and%20raised%20questions%20over%20the%20use%20of%20the%20Marathi%20literary%20meet's%20platform%20for%20political%20mudslinging.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThackeray%2C%20who%20heads%20Sena%20(UBT)%2C%20mocked%20Gorhe%2C%20the%20deputy%20chairperson%20of%20the%20Maharashtra%20Legislative%20Council%2C%20over%20her%20claim.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShow%20me%20where%20those%20cars%20are.%20These%20individuals%20are%20politically%20irrelevant%20to%20me%2C%20and%20I%20do%20not%20wish%20to%20comment%20further.%20She%20is%20a%20woman%2C%20and%20out%20of%20respect%2C%20I%20prefer%20not%20to%20say%20anything%20more%20about%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20reporters%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20row%20escalated%2C%20Gorhe%20said%20her%20comment%20was%20in%20response%20to%20a%20specific%20question.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20didn't%20say%20those%20words%20on%20my%20own%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20a%20news%20channel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGorhe%20claimed%20on%20Saturday%20that%20posts%20in%20the%20undivided%20Sena%20were%20obtained%20through%20corrupt%20means%2C%20including%20gifting%20of%20Mercedes%20cars.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20comments%2C%20made%20at%20the%2098th%20All%20India%20Marathi%20Literary%20Meet%20in%20Delhi%2C%20drew%20sharp%20criticism%20from%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20which%20came%20into%20existence%20following%20a%20split%20in%20original%20Shiv%20Sena.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20MP%20Sanjay%20Raut%20demanded%20an%20explanation%20from%20Akhil%20Bharatiya%20Marathi%20Sahitya%20Mahamandal%2C%20the%20organisers%2C%20over%20the%20appropriateness%20of%20political%20comments%20at%20the%20literary%20gathering.%20He%20wondered%20whether%20the%20event%20was%20held%20under%20some%20political%20pressure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20what%20Gorhe%20said%20was%20true%2C%20then%20there%20would%20have%20been%20a%20line%20of%20Mercedes%20cars%20at%20Matoshree%20(Uddhav%20Thackeray's%20residence)%2C%26quot%3B%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20in%20the%20Legislative%20Council%2C%20Ambadas%20Danve%2C%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20party%20facilitated%20his%20rise%20from%20an%20ordinary%20worker%20in%20Marathwada%20and%20never%20asked%20him%20a%20single%20rupee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGorhe%20only%20filled%20forms%20for%20four%20terms%20(as%20MLC%20when%20she%20was%20a%20member%20of%20the%20undivided%20Sena)%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDanve's%20party%20colleague%2C%20Sushma%20Andhare%2C%20said%20Gorhe%20should%20disclose%20how%20much%20she%20benefitted%20from%20her%20three-decade-long%20association%20with%20the%20undivided%20Shiv%20Sena.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20had%20held%20significant%20influence%20over%20appointments%20when%20she%20was%20in%20undivided%20Sena.%20Going%20by%20her%20claim%20of%20corruption%2C%20she%20should%20account%20for%20her%20earnings%20during%20her%20tenure%2C%26quot%3B%20Andhare%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGorhe%20had%20switched%20her%20allegiance%20to%20the%20Eknath%20Shinde-led%20Shiv%20Sena%20after%20the%20undivided%20Sena%20split%20in%20June%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaut%20demanded%20an%20explanation%20from%20the%20organisers%20of%20the%20Marathi%20literary%20meet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20letter%20to%20Usha%20Tambe%2C%20chairperson%20of%20the%20Akhil%20Bharatiya%20Marathi%20Sahitya%20Mahamandal%2C%20Raut%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BNumerous%20topics%20discussed%20at%20the%2098th%20Literary%20Meet%20were%20unrelated%20to%20literature.%20It%20appears%20that%20the%20event%20was%20held%20under%20some%20political%20pressure.%20The%20platform%20of%20the%20Sahitya%20Mahamandal%20was%20grossly%20misused%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaut%20claimed%20Gorhe%20had%20also%20said%20that%20she%20paid%20Rs%2050%20lakh%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20event%20and%20gifted%20a%20Mercedes%20car%20to%20Tambe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20cannot%20ascertain%20the%20truth%20of%20this%20claim%2C%20but%20such%20comments%20tarnish%20the%20reputation%20of%20the%20Mahamandal%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20stated%20and%20demanded%20an%20apology%20%26quot%3Bif%20the%20event%20was%20not%20organised%20with%20proper%20approval%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20controversy%2C%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20workers%20staged%20a%20protest%20outside%20Gorhe's%20residence%20in%20Pune%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20raised%20slogans%20and%20demanded%20that%20Gorhe%20apologise%20to%20Uddhav%20Thackeray.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20got%20several%20posts%20from%20Thackeray%2C%20but%20once%20she%20changed%20her%20allegiance%2C%20Gorhe%20has%20forgotten%20everything.%20She%20used%20to%20ask%20many%20of%20us%20to%20do%20her%20work%2C%20but%20we%20never%20complained.%20However%2C%20we%20do%20not%20accept%20such%20unfounded%20claims%20of%20Gorhe%20against%20Thackeray%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20protester%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740372780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2Fo0mt0k5_sena_625x300_24_February_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmercedes-for-posts-sena-leaders-corruption-jab-at-uddhav-thackeray-7780997%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Shiv%20Sena%20leader%20Neelam%20Gorhe's%20claim%20on%20allotment%20of%20posts%20in%20the%20erstwhile%20undivided%20Sena%20led%20by%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20after%20gifting%20Mercedes%20cars%20h