0Anil%20Barve.%20Samantha%20will%20also%20make%20her%20debut%20as%20a%20producer%20with%20'Maa%20Inti%20Bangaram'.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fsamantha-ruth-prabhu-the-best-heroines-in-cinema-calls-them-amazing-and-rockstars%2Farticleshow%2F118518663.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bill%20Clinton's%20%26quot%3BReinventing%20Government%26quot%3B%20Saved%20Billions.%20Can%20Trump%20Do%20That%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20new%20administration%20swept%20into%20Washington%20and%20announced%20plans%20to%20shake%20it%20up%2C%20using%20corporate%20know-how%20and%20new%20technology%20to%20streamline%20the%20federal%20bureaucracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20offered%20millions%20of%20government%20employees%20buyouts%20and%20slashed%20costs%20to%20balance%20the%20budget.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20might%20sound%20like%20the%20controversial%20cost-cutting%20push%20led%20by%20billionaire%20Elon%20Musk%20under%20the%20auspices%20of%20Republican%20President%20Donald%20Trump.%20But%20the%20biggest%20effort%20to%20overhaul%20the%20federal%20government%20in%20modern%20history%20actually%20was%2030%20years%20ago%20under%20a%20Democratic%20administration.%20It%20was%20then-President%20Bill%20Clinton's%20%26quot%3B%20Reinventing%20Government%20%26quot%3B%20initiative%2C%20under%20the%20control%20of%20his%20vice%20president%2C%20Al%20Gore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMusk%20himself%20has%20recently%20tried%20to%20associate%20himself%20with%20the%20Clinton%20effort%3A%20%26quot%3BWhat%20%40DOGE%20is%20doing%20is%20similar%20to%20Clinton%2FGore%20Dem%20policies%20of%20the%201990s%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20posted%20on%20his%20social%20platform%20X%2C%20using%20his%20acronym%20for%20the%20effort%20in%20charge%20of%20the%20cuts%2C%20the%20Department%20of%20Government%20Efficiency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20Reinventing%20Government%20project%20was%20nearly%20the%20opposite%20of%20the%20abrupt%2C%20chaotic%20Musk%20effort%2C%20say%20those%20who%20ran%20it%20or%20watched%20it%20unfold.%20It%20was%20authorized%20by%20bipartisan%20congressional%20legislation%2C%20worked%20slowly%20over%20several%20years%20to%20identify%20inefficiencies%20and%20involved%20federal%20workers%20in%20re-envisioning%20their%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20was%20a%20tremendous%20effort%20put%20into%20understanding%20what%20should%20happen%20and%20what%20should%20change%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Max%20Stier%2C%20president%20of%20the%20Partnership%20for%20Public%20Service%2C%20which%20seeks%20to%20improve%20the%20federal%20workforce.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20is%20happening%20now%20is%20actually%20taking%20us%20backwards.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20Musk's%20effort%2C%20the%20Trump%20administration%20has%20fired%20thousands%20of%20federal%20workers%20without%20warning.%20It%20offered%20government%20employees%20a%20%26quot%3B%20deferred%20resignation%26quot%3B%20program%20that%20wasn't%20authorized%20by%20Congress%20and%20gutted%20agencies%20without%20similar%20legislative%20authorization%2C%20though%20sometimes%20judges%20intervened.%20The%20technology%20mogul%20and%20world's%20richest%20person%20has%20pledged%20to%20save%20trillions%20of%20taxpayer%20dollars%20by%20cutting%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThose%20familiar%20with%20the%20Clinton-era%20Reinventing%20Government%20push%20say%20it%20holds%20lessons%20for%20both%20how%20to%20remake%20the%20federal%20bureaucracy%20and%20the%20comparatively%20meager%20savings%20that%20can%20be%20achieved%20from%20such%20an%20effort.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20did%20it%20without%20a%20constitutional%20crisis%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Elaine%20Kamarck%2C%20who%20ran%20Reinventing%20Government%20as%20a%20senior%20Gore%20adviser%20in%20the%201990s.%20%26quot%3BUnlike%20these%20people%2C%20we%20didn't%20think%20there%20were%20vast%20trillions%20in%20efficiencies.%20...%20Their%20mandate%20is%20only%20to%20cut.%20Our%20was%3A%20Works%20better%2C%20costs%20less.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKamarck%20said%20the%20initiative%20grew%20to%20a%20400-person%20staff%20recruited%20from%20existing%20workers%20within%20the%20federal%20agencies.%20They%20set%20about%20making%20the%20government%20more%20efficient%20and%20focused%20on%20customer%20service%2C%20introducing%20private%20sector-style%20metrics%20such%20as%20performance%20standards%20for%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Reinventing%20Government%20team%20also%20pushed%20the%20workforce%20to%20embrace%20a%20brand%20new%20technology%20-%20the%20internet.%20Many%20governmental%20web%20sites%20and%20programs%2C%20including%20the%20electronic%20filing%20of%20income%20taxes%2C%20date%20back%20to%20the%20Reinventing%20Government%20initiative.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGore%20appeared%20on%20the%20David%20Letterman%20late%20night%20television%20show%20and%20smashed%20a%20government%20ash%20tray%20with%20a%20hammer%20to%20symbolize%20his%20crusade%20to%20eliminate%20waste.%20The%20government%20ended%20up%20giving%20out%20%26quot%3Bhammer%20awards%26quot%3B%20to%20employees%20who%20came%20up%20with%20ways%20to%20cut%20red%20tape%20and%20improve%20service%2C%20recalled%20Don%20Kettl%2C%20an%20emeritus%20professor%20of%20public%20policy%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Maryland.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLiberating%20employees%20and%20seeing%20employees%20as%20a%20better%20part%20of%20the%20system%20was%20a%20big%20piece%20of%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Kettl%20recalled.%20%26quot%3BOne%20important%20difference%20is%20the%20Trump%20administration%20sees%20federal%20employees%20as%20the%20bad%20guys%2C%20and%20the%20Clinton%20administration%20saw%20federal%20employees%20as%20good%20guys.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Clinton%20administration%20also%20worked%20with%20Congress%20to%20authorize%20%2425%2C000%20buyouts%20for%20federal%20workers%20and%20ended%20up%20eliminating%20what%20Kamarck%20said%20were%20more%20than%20400%2C000%20federal%20positions%20between%201993%20and%202000%20through%20a%20combination%20of%20voluntary%20departures%2C%20attrition%20and%20a%20relatively%20small%20number%20of%20layoffs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKettl%20said%20the%20job%20cuts%20didn't%20save%20money%20because%20the%20government%20had%20to%20turn%20around%20and%20hire%20contractors%20to%20perform%20the%20tasks%20of%20workers%20who%20left%20-%20something%20he%20worries%20will%20happen%20again%20if%20Musk%20and%20Trump%20continue%20to%20slash%20the%20federal%20workforce.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChris%20Edwards%2C%20who%20edits%20DownsizingGovernment.org%20at%20the%20conservative%20Cato%20Institute%20in%20Washington%2C%20said%20buyouts%20symbolize%20the%20important%20difference%20between%20the%20Clinton%20effort%2C%20which%20he%20called%20%26quot%3Bmoderately%20successful%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20current%20DOGE%20campaign%20-%20the%20involvement%20of%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Republicans%20who%20control%20Congress%20today%20have%20let%20Musk%20move%20ahead%20with%20his%20changes%20without%20them%2C%20even%20though%20the%20Constitution%20states%20that%20the%20legislative%20branch%20approves%20spending%20and%20federal%20law%20prohibits%20the%20president%20from%20cutting%20programs%20Congress%20has%20authorized%20without%20its%20permission.%20Clinton%20was%20the%20last%20president%20to%20successfully%20seek%20that%20permission%2C%20with%20Congress%20accepting%20%243.6%20billion%20in%20cuts%20he%20proposed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20and%20Musk%20have%20made%20only%20vague%20promises%20about%20submitting%20cuts%20to%20Congress.%20Without%20its%20involvement%2C%20any%20savings%20will%20be%20fleeting%2C%20Edwards%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BNone%20of%20these%20changes%20DOGE%20wants%20to%20make%20will%20be%20permanent%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFew%20Republicans%20have%20suggested%20greater%20involvement%20by%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20requires%20speaking%20out.%20It%20requires%20saying%2C%20'That%20violates%20the%20law%2C%20that%20violates%20the%20authorities%20of%20the%20executive%2C'%26quot%3B%20said%20Sen.%20Lisa%20Murkowski%2C%20R-Alaska.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKamarck%20estimated%20the%20total%20savings%20of%20Reinventing%20Government%20at%20%24146%20billion%20-%20a%20considerable%20amount%2C%20but%20still%20only%20a%20tiny%20sliver%20of%20the%20federal%20budget.%20She%20contrasted%20the%20slow%2C%20deliberative%20and%20collaborative%20approach%20her%20team%20took%20with%20Musk's%20breakneck%20pace%2C%20led%20by%20a%20team%20of%20young%20outsiders%20he%20has%20brought%20in%20to%20slash%20agencies%20and%20their%20workforce.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reason%20Reinventing%20Government%20moved%20slowly%2C%20Kamarck%20said%2C%20was%20that%20it%20didn't%20want%20to%20interfere%20with%20the%20myriad%20crucial%20roles%20of%20government%20while%20restructuring%20it.%20Musk%20seems%20to%20have%20few%20such%20concerns%2C%20she%20fears.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20stakes%20in%20federal%20government%20failure%20are%20really%2C%20really%20high%20in%20a%20way%20they're%20not%20in%20the%20private%20sector%2C%26quot%3B%20Kamarck%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20really%20worried%20about%20screwing%20things%20up%2C%20and%20I%20don't%20think%20these%20guys%20are%20worried%20enough%20about%20screwing%20things%20up%2C%20and%20it'll%20be%20their%20undoing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740366720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Frnsc5se_bill-clinton_625x300_23_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbill-clintons-reinventing-government-saved-billions-can-donald-trump-do-that-7780471%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20n