of%20Kolkata%20on%20February%2019%20morning%20when%20the%20cops%20reached%20there%20to%20investigate%20the%20accident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20suspicion%20of%20the%20two%20brothers%20murdering%20the%20two%20women%20and%20the%20minor%20has%20surfaced%20since%20the%20autopsy%20reports%20of%20the%20three%20have%20ruled%20out%20the%20possibility%20of%20suicide%2C%20which%20was%20initially%20suspected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20sources%20from%20the%20city%20police%20said%20an%20initial%20investigation%20revealed%20that%20the%20Dey%20family%2C%20owning%20a%20leather%20goods%20business%2C%20had%20accumulated%20huge%20debts%2C%20which%20might%20have%20prompted%20the%20two%20brothers%20to%20take%20such%20a%20drastic%20step.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInvestigation%20and%20interrogation%20of%20some%20of%20the%20close%20associates%20of%20the%20family%2C%20city%20police%20sources%20added%2C%20had%20also%20revealed%20that%20despite%20the%20huge%20accumulated%20debt%20on%20them%20the%20two%20brothers%20did%20not%20curtail%20their%20lavish%20lifestyles%20which%20led%20to%20the%20rising%20debt%20further.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20women%2C%20who%20are%20suspected%20to%20be%20murdered%2C%20are%20Romi%20Dey%20and%20Sudeshna%20Dey.%20While%20Romi%20is%20the%20wife%20of%20Prasun%20De%2C%20the%20other%20woman%20is%20Pranay%20Dey's%20spouse.%20The%20minor%20Priyamvada%20Dey%20(14)%20is%20the%20daughter%20of%20Prasun%20and%20Romi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECity%20police%20sources%20said%20that%20on%20the%20day%20of%20the%20murders%2C%20all%20the%20CCTV%20machines%20installed%20within%20the%20residence%20were%20switched%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740366420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2Fcq3r7mt8_kolkata-murdersuicide-women_625x300_20_February_25.