20moments.%20But%20it's%20an%20interesting%20way%20of%20endearing%20Black%2C%20who%20is%20ruthless%20at%20work%2C%20to%20the%20audience.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsuits-la-ted-black-brother-twist-explained-2025-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740366121000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67b774787bb3f854015d61f9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsuits-la-ted-black-brother-twist-explained-2025-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20first%20episode%20of%20%26quot%3BSuits%20LA%26quot%3B%20ends%20with%20a%20revelation%20about%20Ted%20Black%20and%20his%20family.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ejacobs%40insider.com%20(Eammon%20Jacobs)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A67%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsuits-la-ted-black-brother-twist-explained-2025-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BTrying%20To%20Get%20Money%20Back%20Or%20Secured%26quot%3B%3A%20Donald%20Trump%20On%20Ukraine%20Aid%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUS%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20said%20on%20Saturday%20he%20was%20trying%20to%20get%20money%20back%20for%20the%20billions%20of%20dollars%20sent%20to%20support%20Ukraine's%20war%20against%20Russia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20comments%20came%20as%20Washington%20and%20Kyiv%20negotiate%20a%20mineral%20resources%20deal%20Trump%20wants%20as%20compensation%20for%20the%20wartime%20aid%20his%20predecessor%20Joe%20Biden%20gave%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20the%20latest%20twist%20in%20a%20whirlwind%20first%20month%20since%20he%20took%20office%2C%20during%20which%20he%20has%20upended%20US%20foreign%20policy%20by%20making%20diplomatic%20overtures%20towards%20the%20Kremlin%20over%20the%20heads%20of%20Ukraine%20and%20Europe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20told%20delegates%20at%20the%20Conservative%20Political%20Action%20Conference%20(CPAC)%20near%20Washington%3A%20%26quot%3BI'm%20trying%20to%20get%20the%20money%20back%2C%20or%20secured.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20want%20them%20to%20give%20us%20something%20for%20all%20of%20the%20money%20that%20we%20put%20up.%20We're%20asking%20for%20rare%20earth%20and%20oil%2C%20anything%20we%20can%20get.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20going%20to%20get%20our%20money%20back%20because%20it's%20just%20not%20fair.%20And%20we%20will%20see%2C%20but%20I%20think%20we're%20pretty%20close%20to%20a%20deal%2C%20and%20we%20better%20be%20close%20because%20that%20has%20been%20a%20horrible%20situation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHours%20earlier%2C%20a%20source%20told%20AFP%20that%20Ukrainian%20President%20Volodymyr%20Zelensky%20was%20%26quot%3Bnot%20ready%26quot%3B%20to%20sign%20such%20a%20deal%2C%20despite%20growing%20US%20pressure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWar%20of%20words%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump's%20special%20envoy%20Keith%20Kellogg%2C%20who%20met%20Zelensky%20this%20week%2C%20said%20the%20Ukrainian%20president%20understood%20signing%20a%20deal%20with%20the%20United%20States%20was%20%26quot%3Bcritical.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20Ukrainian%20source%20told%20AFP%20that%20Kyiv%20needed%20assurances%20first.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20form%20in%20which%20the%20draft%20is%20now%2C%20the%20president%20is%20not%20ready%20to%20accept%2C%20we%20are%20still%20trying%20to%20make%20changes%20and%20add%20constructiveness%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20source%20close%20to%20the%20matter%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUkraine%20wants%20any%20agreement%20signed%20with%20the%20United%20States%20to%20include%20security%20guarantees%20as%20it%20battles%20Russia's%20nearly%20three-year%20invasion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20negotiations%20between%20the%20two%20countries%20come%20amid%20a%20deepening%20war%20of%20words%20between%20Trump%20and%20Zelensky%20that%20has%20raised%20alarm%20in%20Kyiv%20and%20Europe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20Trump%20branded%20his%20Ukrainian%20counterpart%20a%20%26quot%3Bdictator%26quot%3B%20and%20called%20for%20him%20to%20%26quot%3Bmove%20fast%26quot%3B%20to%20end%20the%20war%2C%20a%20day%20after%20Russian%20and%20US%20officials%20held%20talks%20in%20Saudi%20Arabia%20without%20Kyiv.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWashington%20has%20proposed%20a%20United%20Nations%20resolution%20on%20the%20Ukraine%20conflict%20that%20omitted%20any%20mention%20of%20Kyiv's%20territory%20occupied%20by%20Russia%2C%20diplomatic%20sources%20told%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'What%20kind%20of%20partnership%20is%20this%3F'%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20has%20asked%20for%20%26quot%3B%24500%20billion%20worth%26quot%3B%20of%20rare%20earth%20minerals%20to%20make%20up%20for%20aid%20given%20to%20Kyiv%20--%20a%20price%20tag%20Ukraine%20has%20balked%20at%20and%20which%20is%20much%20higher%20than%20published%20US%20aid%20figures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20no%20American%20obligations%20in%20the%20agreement%20regarding%20guarantees%20or%20investments%2C%20everything%20about%20them%20is%20very%20vague%2C%20and%20they%20want%20to%20extract%20%24500%20billion%20from%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Ukrainian%20source%20told%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20kind%20of%20partnership%20is%20this%3F%20And%20why%20do%20we%20have%20to%20give%20%24500%20billion%2C%20there%20is%20no%20answer%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20source%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20Ukraine%20had%20proposed%20changes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20United%20States%20has%20given%20Ukraine%20more%20than%20%2460%20billion%20in%20military%20aid%20since%20Russia's%20invasion%2C%20according%20to%20official%20figures%20--%20the%20largest%20such%20contribution%20among%20Kyiv's%20allies%20but%20substantially%20lower%20than%20Trump's%20figures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Kiel%20Institute%2C%20a%20German%20economic%20research%20body%2C%20said%20that%20from%202022%20until%20the%20end%20of%202024%2C%20the%20United%20States%20gave%20a%20total%20of%20114.2%20billion%20euros%20(%24119.8%20billion)%20in%20financial%2C%20humanitarian%20and%20military%20aid.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EUK%20support%20'ironclad'%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20senior%20Ukrainian%20official%20told%20AFP%20Friday%20that%20despite%20the%20tensions%2C%20talks%20on%20a%20possible%20agreement%20were%20%26quot%3Bongoing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20row%20comes%20as%20Ukraine%20is%20set%20to%20mark%20the%20third%20anniversary%20of%20Russia's%20invasion%20on%20Monday%2C%20and%20as%20Kyiv's%20forces%20are%20slowly%20ceding%20ground%20on%20the%20front%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoscow's%20defense%20ministry%20earlier%20on%20Saturday%20claimed%20the%20capture%20of%20Novolyubivka%20in%20the%20eastern%20Lugansk%20region%2C%20which%20is%20now%20largely%20under%20Russian%20control.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20call%20with%20Zelensky%20on%20Saturday%2C%20British%20Prime%20Minister%20Keir%20Starmer%20pledged%20the%20%26quot%3BUK's%20ironclad%20support%20for%20Ukraine%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZelensky%2C%20in%20response%2C%20praised%20the%20United%20Kingdom%20for%20showing%20%26quot%3Bleadership%26quot%3B%20on%20the%20war%20with%20Russia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStarmer%20also%20said%20it%20was%20in%20the%20%26quot%3Binterests%26quot%3B%20of%20both%20Britain%20and%20the%20United%20States%20to%20%26quot%3Bstand%20by%26quot%3B%20Ukraine%2C%20which%20needed%20a%20seat%20at%20the%20negotiating%20table%20and%20%26quot%3Bstrong%20security%20guarantees%20so%20the%20peace%20will%20last%26quot%3B%2C%20writing%20in%20a%20column%20for%20The%20Sun%20published%20late%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EForeign%20Secretary%20David%20Lammy%20announced%20that%20Britain%20will%20unveil%20a%20significant%20package%20of%20sanctions%20against%20Russia%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20London%2C%20thousands%20of%20people%20marched%20in%20support%20of%20Ukraine%20on%20Saturday%2C%20and%20polls%20