2originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236316779%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Zoe%20Salda%C3%B1a%20continued%20her%20awards%20season%20sweep%20for%20best%20supporting%20actress%20by%20taking%20home%20the%20SAG%20Award%20for%20her%20performance%20as%20Rita%20in%20%E2%80%9CEmilia%20P%C3%A9rez.%E2%80%9D%20She%20has%20now%20was%20supporting%20actress%20prizes%20from%20all%20the%20major%20Oscar%20precursor%20awards%3A%20Golden%20Globes%2C%20Critics%E2%80%99%20Choice%2C%20BAFTAs%20and%20SAG.%20These%20wins%20make%20Salda%C3%B1a%20the%20clear%20frontrunner%20to%20win%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Zack%20Sharf%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2025%2Ffilm%2Fawards%2Fzoe-saldana-sag-award-supporting-actress-1236316779%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Who%20Is%20Friedrich%20Merz%2C%20Poised%20to%20Be%20Germany's%20Next%20Chancellor%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFriedrich%20Merz%2C%20a%20man%20who%20has%20never%20held%20a%20government%20role%2C%20is%20preparing%20to%20take%20the%20reins%20in%20Germany%20just%20as%20the%20country%20faces%20its%20biggest%20economic%20and%20diplomatic%20crises%20in%20decades%20and%20Europe%20looks%20urgently%20for%20a%20new%20generation%20of%20leaders%20for%20an%20era%20of%20transatlantic%20tension.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMerz's%20conservatives%20came%20first%20in%20Germany's%20national%20election%20on%20Sunday%2C%20according%20to%20projected%20results%2C%20well%20ahead%20of%20their%20closest%20rival%2C%20the%20far-right%20Alternative%20for%20Germany%20(AfD)%2C%20giving%20him%20a%20mandate%20to%20form%20a%20coalition%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGermany%20will%20once%20more%20be%20governed%20reliably%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20supporters%20on%20Sunday%20evening.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20results%20spell%20an%20unlikely%20third-act%20triumph%20for%20the%2069-year-old%2C%20who%20just%20seven%20years%20ago%20was%20seen%20as%20a%20failed%20politician%20fully%20reconciled%20to%20ending%20his%20career%20as%20a%20wealthy%20lobbyist%20and%20member%20of%20numerous%20company%20boards.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20protege%20of%20the%20late%20Wolfgang%20Schaeuble%2C%20finance%20minister%20and%20icon%20of%20German%20fiscal%20conservatism%2C%20Merz%20enjoyed%20a%20meteoric%20rise%20through%20his%20Christian%20Democrats%2C%20becoming%20the%20party's%20parliamentary%20leader%20in%20the%202000s.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETall%20and%20with%20a%20sonorous%20voice%2C%20the%20arch-conservative%20Merz%20was%20a%20perfect%20figure%20for%20the%20party%20in%201989%20-%20when%20he%20first%20won%20elected%20office%20for%20the%20European%20Parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHailing%20from%20the%20Sauerland%2C%20a%20Catholic%20upland%20region%20in%20far%20western%20Germany%20known%20for%20its%20social%20conservatism%20and%20close-knit%20village%20communities%2C%20he%20embodied%20many%20of%20the%20virtues%20of%20West%20Germany%20before%20the%20fall%20of%20the%20Berlin%20Wall%20-%20transatlanticist%2C%20business-oriented%20and%20socially%20conservative.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20reunification%20in%201990%20allowed%20Angela%20Merkel%2C%20the%20East%20German%20daughter%20of%20a%20protestant%20pastor%2C%20to%20enter%20politics%20and%20elbow%20both%20Schaeuble%20and%20Merz%20aside%20on%20her%20rise%20to%20become%20chancellor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20east%20continues%20to%20be%20Merz's%20weak%20spot.%20A%20Forsa%20poll%20on%20Friday%20showed%20that%20unlike%20his%20Social%20Democrat%20and%20Green%20rivals%2C%20this%20distinctly%20Rhineland%20figure%20is%20still%20far%20less%20trusted%20in%20the%20east%20than%20the%20west.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20also%20the%20east%20that%20gave%20rise%20to%20the%20greatest%20challenge%20to%20Merz's%20authority%20in%20the%20guise%20of%20the%20far-right%20AfD%2C%20which%20took%20first%20place%20in%20one%20eastern%20regional%20election%20last%20year%20and%20could%20yet%20greatly%20constrain%20his%20ability%20to%20govern%20after%20the%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENever%20the%20favourite%20of%20his%20party's%20professional%20advisers%2C%20Merz%20was%20twice%20rejected%20as%20Merkel's%20successor%20as%20party%20leader%2C%20in%202018%20and%202021%2C%20before%20his%20doggedness%20won%20out%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20took%20office%20pledging%20to%20kill%20off%20the%20nativist%20AfD%20by%20breaking%20with%20Merkel's%20centrism%20and%20moving%20the%20party%20rightwards.%20The%20AfD%2C%20on%2010%25%20when%20he%20took%20office%2C%20won%20some%2020%25%20in%20Sunday's%20election%2C%20according%20to%20projected%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20do%20politics%20so%20that%20a%20party%20like%20the%20AfD%20is%20no%20longer%20needed%20in%20Germany%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20a%20congress%20of%20his%20conservatives%20in%20January%2C%20blaming%20the%20Social%20Democrat%20Scholz%20and%20his%20Green%20partners%20for%20creating%20the%20conditions%20that%20nurtured%20the%20AfD.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20January%2C%20responding%20to%20two%20high-profile%20killings%20in%20which%20immigrants%20were%20the%20main%20suspects%2C%20he%20manoeuvred%20to%20get%20a%20resolution%20demanding%20a%20clampdown%20on%20migration%20through%20parliament%2C%20knowing%20that%20it%20would%20only%20pass%20with%20AfD%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECritics%2C%20even%20in%20his%20own%20ranks%2C%20saw%20this%20as%20an%20unforgivable%20breach%20of%20a%20political%20quarantine%20designed%20to%20keep%20the%20AfD%20out%20of%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20some%2C%20it%20was%20a%20case%20of%20Merz's%20strategic%20sense%20not%20matching%20the%20acute%20tactical%20skills%20that%20enabled%20him%20to%20repeatedly%20pin%20down%20Scholz%2C%20first%20with%20a%202022%20visit%20to%20Kyiv%20that%20exposed%20the%20chancellor's%20hesitancy%20on%20supporting%20Ukraine%2C%20and%20then%20by%20getting%20a%20court%20to%20strike%20down%20a%20budget%2C%20setting%20in%20motion%20the%20chain%20of%20events%20that%20collapsed%20Scholz's%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20migration%20vote%20created%20a%20lingering%20sense%20of%20distrust%2C%20and%20fueled%20concerns%20that%20he%20may%20struggle%20to%20persuade%20other%20parties%20to%20govern%20with%20him%2C%20a%20necessity%20in%20Germany's%20proportional%20electoral%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20want%20to%20suggest%20Merz%20plans%20(a%20coalition%20with%20the%20AfD)%2C%20but%20I%20have%20to%20say%20my%20personal%20confidence%20that%20he%20won't%20do%20it%20after%20the%20election%20if%20that's%20his%20only%20way%20of%20becoming%20Chancellor%20-%20that's%20gone%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ulf%20Buermeyer%2C%20host%20of%20the%20popular%20and%20influential%20podcast%20State%20of%20the%20Nation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ETHE%20PRICE%20OF%20POLITICS%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20internal%20critics%20grudgingly%20sense%20his%20Atlanticism%2C%20excellent%20spoken%20English%20and%20negotiating%20skills%20honed%20in%20the%20boardrooms%20in%20which%20he%20served%20during%20his%20political%20hiatus%20make%20him%20a%20good%20candidate%20for%20the%20Trump%20era.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20early%20and%20outspoken%20backer%20of%20supporting%20Ukraine%20in%20its%20war%20against%20Russia%2C%20he%20has%20said%20he%20would%20under%20some%20circumstances%20send%20Kyiv%20the%20high-end%20Taurus%20missiles%20that%20Scholz%20has%20always%20blocked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20fiscal%20policy%2C%20his%20policies%20are%20equally%20ill-defined%2C%20but%20he%20has%20suggested%20he%20is%20open%20to%20reforming%20constitutionally-enshrined%20debt%20limits%20that%20doomed%20Scholz's%20government%20and%20have%20hampered%20attempts%20to%20boost%20military%20spending.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20all%20that%2C%20he%20is%20in%20many%20ways%20an%20old-fashioned%20figure%20from%20the%20time%20before%20he%20left%20politics%20for%20a%20lucrative%20second%20career%20at%20Blackrock%20that%20made%20the%20hobby%20pilot%20wealthy%20enough%20to%20own%20an%20aeroplane.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParts%20of%20his%20policy%20agenda%20are%20reactive%3A%20he%20has%20pledged%20to%20scrap%20an%20unemployment%20benefit%20and%20easier%20citizenship%20rules%20introduced%20by%20Scholz's%20coalition%2C%20and%20to%20introduce%20tougher%20border%20controls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20once%20told%20an%20interviewer%20that%20he%20would%20leave%20politics%20if%20it%20ever%20placed%20his%2040-year-marriage%2C%20to%20Charlotte%2C%20a%20judge%2C%20under%20strain.%20%26quot%3BFor%20me%20that%20price%20would%20be%20too%20high%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20he%20takes%20office%2C%20he%20will%20be%20the%20first%20chancellor%20with%20children%2C%20and%20the%20first%20not%20previously%20divorced%2C%20since%20Helmut%20Kohl%20left%20office%20in%201998.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20been%20assiduous%20about%20building%20contacts%20with%20the%20European%20leaders%20who%20would%20be%20his%20peers%2C%20with%20some%20welcoming%20the%20prospect%20of%20an%20end%20to%20Scholz's%20divided%20and%20indecisive%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAlmost%20undiplomatic%2C%26quot%3B%20was%20how%20one%20European%20diplomat%20described%20the%20enthusiasm%20with%20which%20Paris%20was%20awaiting%20Merz's%20arrival.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20weekend's%20Munich%20Security%20Conference%20saw%20him%20doing%20the%20rounds%20of%20European%20leaders%20and%20holding%20meetings%20with%20U.S.%20Vice-President%20JD%20Vance%20and%20Chinese%20Foreign%20Minister%20Wang%20Yi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20world%20leaders%20may%20have%20to%20wait%3A%20with%20polls%20showing%20a%20real%20chance%20of%20a%20parliament%20with%20as%20many%20as%20seven%20parties%2C%20Germany%20could%20be%20in%20for%20many%20months%20of%20fractious%20coalition%20talks%20before%20Merz%20walks%20into%20Berlin's%20riverside%20chancellery.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%