D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F582636a3dd08952f4b8b4a25%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWarren%20Buffett%2C%20the%20CEO%20and%20chairman%20of%20Berkshire%20Hathaway%2C%20shared%20more%20than%20just%20financial%20details%20in%20the%20company's%20annual%20shareholder%20letter.%3Cp%3EReuters%2FMario%20Anzuoni%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-warren-buffett-spends-money-net-worth%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWarren%20Buffett%3C%2Fa%3E%20includes%20some%20business%20lessons%20in%20his%20latest%20shareholder%20letter%2C%20published%20Saturday.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBuffett%20said%20mistakes%20will%20happen.%20It's%20owning%20up%20to%20them%20that's%20important.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20also%20advised%20against%20judging%20candidates%20by%20education%2C%20stressing%20the%20value%20of%20innate%20talent.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EEvery%20year%2C%20executives%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Fwhat-is-ipo%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epublicly%20traded%20companies%3C%2Fa%3E%20draft%20letters%20to%20their%20shareholders.%20These%20letters%20summarize%20the%20company's%20operations%2C%20detailing%20its%20annual%20financial%20results%2C%20major%20wins%20and%20losses%2C%20and%20outlook%20for%20the%20coming%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20perhaps%20no%20annual%20letter%20more%20anticipated%20than%20the%20one%20Warren%20Buffett%20sends%20to%20his%20Berkshire%20Hathaway%20shareholders.%20Investors%20and%20business%20leaders%20scour%20the%20letter%20for%20hints%20about%20the%20economy%20and%20financial%20strategies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20also%2C%20however%2C%20often%20includes%20some%20more%20fundamental%20business%20%E2%80%94%20and%20life%20%E2%80%94%20lessons%2C%20too.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Buffett's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwarren-buffett-letter-berkshire-hathaway-taxes-government-waste-stocks-cash-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elatest%20shareholder%20letter%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20published%20on%20Saturday%2C%20he%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BIn%20addition%20to%20the%20mandated%20data%2C%20we%20believe%20we%20owe%20you%20additional%20commentary%20about%20what%20you%20own%20and%20how%20we%20think.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20read%20through%20this%20year's%20letter%20to%20gather%20Buffett's%20best%20insights.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2260bbd338-9774-4a3e-947d-5d282e0f4528%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMistakes%20happen.%20Own%20up%20to%20them%20before%20it's%20too%20late.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBuffett%20said%20he's%20made%20many%20mistakes%20over%20the%20years.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20have%20stemmed%20from%20incorrectly%20assessing%20the%20%26quot%3Bfuture%20economics%26quot%3B%20of%20companies%20he%20purchased%20for%20Berkshire%20Hathaway.%20Others%20have%20come%20from%20hiring%20the%20wrong%20managers%20%E2%80%94%20miscalculating%20either%20their%20abilities%20or%20loyalty%20to%20the%20organization.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBetween%202019%20and%202023%2C%20Buffett%20wrote%20that%20he%20used%20the%20word%20%26quot%3Bmistake%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Berror%26quot%3B%2016%20times%20in%20his%20annual%20shareholder%20letter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20point%20is%20that%20mistakes%20are%20normal%20in%20the%20course%20of%20doing%20business.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20cardinal%20sin%20is%20delaying%20the%20correction%20of%20mistakes%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229262cae4-ddfb-4144-9f13-641f8ce4f74c%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EKnow%20the%20power%20of%20a%20'single%20winning%20decision.'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Buffett%2C%20the%20corollary%20to%20acknowledging%20mistakes%20is%20recognizing%20the%20power%20of%20big%20wins.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20experience%20is%20that%20a%20single%20winning%20decision%20can%20make%20a%20breathtaking%20difference%20over%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20pointed%20to%20several%20key%20moments%20in%20Berkshire%20Hathaway's%20history%20%E2%80%94%20the%20strategic%20acquisition%20of%20GEICO%2C%20the%20decision%20to%20bring%20former%20McKinsey%20consultant%20Ajit%20Jain%20into%20management%2C%20and%20finding%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcharlie-mungers-best-business-advice-over-the-years-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECharlie%20Munger%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Buffett's%20longtime%20friend%20and%20business%20partner%2C%20who%20served%20as%20vice%20chairman%20of%20the%20conglomerate%20for%20more%20than%20four%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMistakes%20fade%20away%3B%20winners%20can%20forever%20blossom%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220d0775cc-9e3b-4acb-8792-dd92168117e3%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ENever%20judge%20a%20candidate%20by%20their%20educational%20background.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20selecting%20a%20CEO%2C%20Buffett%20has%20a%20rule%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20never%20look%20at%20where%20a%20candidate%20has%20gone%20to%20school.%20Never!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBuffett%20pointed%20to%20the%20case%20of%20Pete%20Liegl%2C%20the%20founder%20and%20manager%20of%20Forest%20River%2C%20an%20RV%20manufacturing%20company%20that%20Berkshire%20Hathaway%20acquired%20in%202005.%20In%20the%2019%20years%20following%20the%20acquisition%2C%20Buffett%20said%20Liegl%20far%20surpassed%20his%20competitors%20in%20performance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20great%20managers%20who%20attended%20the%20most%20famous%20schools.%20But%20there%20are%20plenty%2C%20such%20as%20Pete%2C%20who%20may%20have%20benefited%20by%20attending%20a%20less%20prestigious%20institution%20or%20even%20by%20not%20bothering%20to%20finish%20school%2C%26quot%3B%20Buffett%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBuffett's%20takeaway%20is%20that%20%26quot%3Ba%20very%20large%20portion%20of%20business%20talent%20is%20innate%20with%20nature%20swamping%20nurture.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e3d8405e-5ae0-4ada-bcd2-2ff8453017be%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EKeep%20saving.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBuffett%20believes%20that%20a%20long-standing%20culture%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbanking%2Fhow-to-save-money%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaving%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20and%20reinvesting%20%E2%80%94%20has%20been%20a%20key%20to%20the%20success%20of%20American%20capitalism.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20country's%20founding%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20needed%20many%20Americans%20to%20consistently%20save%20and%20then%20needed%20those%20savers%20or%20other%20Americans%20to%20wisely%20deploy%20the%20capital%20thus%20made%20available%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BIf%20America%20had%20consumed%20all%20that%20it%20produced%2C%20the%20country%20would%20have%20been%20spinning%20its%20wheels.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELikewise%2C%20Berkshire%20Hathaway's%20shareholders%20have%20%26quot%3Bparticipated%20in%20the%20American%20miracle%26quot%3B%20by%20reinvesting%20their%20dividends%2C%20as%20opposed%20to%20consuming%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20ensure%20citizens%20continue%20to%20save%20and%20the%20country%20prospers%2C%20Buffett%20shared%20some%20advice%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Fwhat-is-the-federal-reserve%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eregulators%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20%26quot%3BNever%20forget%20that%20we%20need%20you%20to%20maintain%20a%20stable%20currency%20and%20that%20result%20requires%20both%20wisdom%20and%20vigilance%20on%20your%20part.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwarren-buffett-shareholder-letter-wisdom-management-2025-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22pu