-fear-doge-productivity-email-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDOGE's%20email%20left%20them%20frustrated%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20fearful%20of%20losing%20their%20jobs.%20One%20told%20BI%20the%20action%20felt%20like%20%26quot%3Bharassment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fin%2Flisadownerrigoli%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELisa%20Rigoli%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20human%20resources%20strategist%20and%20leadership%20coach%20who%20founded%20Elements%20of%20Change%2C%20a%20group%20focused%20on%20HR%20consultation%20and%20leadership%20coaching%2C%20said%20the%20email%20lacked%20emotional%20intelligence%20and%20prioritized%20%26quot%3Befficiency%20over%20human-centered%20leadership.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20clear%20example%20of%20how%20leaders%20are%20becoming%20increasingly%20disconnected%20from%20the%20emotional%20impact%20of%20their%20decisions%2C%26quot%3B%20Rigoli%20said.%20%26quot%3BBusiness%20schools%20and%20leadership%20programs%20do%20a%20great%20job%20preparing%20executives%20intellectually%2C%20but%20very%20few%20equip%20them%20for%20the%20emotional%20demands%20of%20leadership.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETamanna%20Ramesh%2C%20founder%20of%20professional%20training%20service%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsparkcareers.us%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESpark%20Careers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20said%20such%20tactics%20could%20damage%20staff%20morale.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRequiring%20employees%20to%20justify%20their%20jobs%20through%20a%20weekly%20report%20%E2%80%94%20under%20the%20threat%20of%20termination%20%E2%80%94%20is%20fear-based%20management.%20It%20doesn't%20drive%20innovation%20or%20efficiency.%20It%20fuels%20resentment%2C%20disengagement%2C%20and%20quiet%20quitting%2C%26quot%3B%20Ramesh%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BAccountability%20matters%2C%20but%20when%20employees%20feel%20like%20they're%20on%20trial%20rather%20than%20trusted%20contributors%2C%20performance%20suffers.%